<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lustily" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lustily,</orth> spiritedly: <cit><quote>she hears them chant it l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 869" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 869</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>let's tune, and to it l. awhile,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 2, 25</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I determine to fight l. for him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.201" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 201</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you have rung it l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 14</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>